  <entry>
    <title>SSR+WS+VNET—_Tunnel隧道加密节点搭建</title>
    <url>/2020/05/01/SSR-WS-VNET%E2%80%94-Tunnel%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%93%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>1：在国外VPS{服务端}SERVER安装Vnet_Tunnel，脚本如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum -y install zip unzip</span><br><span class="line">wget -N --no-check-certificate <span class="string">"https://github.com/siemenstutorials/Vnet_tunnel/raw/master/tunnel.zip"</span> &amp;&amp; unzip tunnel.zip &amp;&amp; chmod -R +x ./*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>2：让Vnet_Tunnel后台运行，脚本如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nohup ./server &gt;&gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>3：Server后台面板登陆：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">server服务器IP:8081/resources/add_server.html</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>4:在国内VPS{客户端}Client安装Vnet_Tunnel，服本如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum -y install zip unzip</span><br><span class="line">wget -N --no-check-certificate <span class="string">"https://github.com/siemenstutorials/Vnet_tunnel/raw/master/tunnel.zip"</span> &amp;&amp; unzip tunnel.zip &amp;&amp; chmod -R +x ./*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>5:后台运行Client,运行如下脚本：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nohup ./client &gt;&gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>6:开启防火墙流量转发：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl  start   firewalld.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>7:开启路由转发功能和流量伪装:</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> 1 &gt; /proc/sys/net/ipv4/ip_forward</span><br><span class="line">sysctl -p</span><br><span class="line">firewall-cmd --zone=public --permanent --add-masquerade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>8:开启端口</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firewall-cmd --add-port=1112/tcp --permanent</span><br><span class="line">firewall-cmd --add-port=nat端口/tcp --permanent</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>9：将NAT端口流量转发至1112</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firewall-cmd --add-forward-port=port=nat端口:proto=tcp:toaddr=nat内网ip:toport=1112 --permanent</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>10:重载防火墙</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firewall-cmd --reload</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>11:后台面板登陆：<br>服务器IP:NAT指定外部通讯端口/resources/add_client.html</p>
<p>12:NAT TUNNEL服务端设置好后切记得关闭防火墙否则无法FQ<br>防火墙关闭命令</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl stop firewalld</span><br><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">disable</span> firewalld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
